lead_paragraph: Chris Narveson combined with four relievers on a two-hitter, leading the Miami Marlins over the New York Mets 1-0 on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Narveson, 4 Relievers Pitch 2-Hitter; Marlins Beat Mets 1-0
